trans-unit.source: A class that represents the syndication versions supported by Windows Communication Foundation (WCF).
trans-unit.target: Uma classe que representa as versões de sindicalização compatíveis com o WCF (Windows Communication Foundation).

trans-unit.source: This class represents the syndication versions that [!INCLUDE[indigo2](~/includes/indigo2-md.md)] supports by default.
trans-unit.target: Essa classe representa as versões de distribuição que [!INCLUDE[indigo2](~/includes/indigo2-md.md)] suporta por padrão.

trans-unit.source: You can add support for additional syndication versions by implementing your own <xref:System.ServiceModel.Syndication.SyndicationFeed>, <xref:System.ServiceModel.Syndication.SyndicationItem>, and <xref:System.ServiceModel.Syndication.SyndicationFeedFormatter> classes.
trans-unit.target: Você pode adicionar suporte para versões de distribuição adicionais ao implementar seu próprio <xref:System.ServiceModel.Syndication.SyndicationFeed>, <xref:System.ServiceModel.Syndication.SyndicationItem>, e <xref:System.ServiceModel.Syndication.SyndicationFeedFormatter> classes.

trans-unit.source: Represents support for the Atom 1.0 specification.
trans-unit.target: Representa suporte para a especificação Atom 1.0.

trans-unit.source: Represents support for the RSS 2.0 specification.
trans-unit.target: Representa suporte para a especificação RSS 2.0.
